<div class="modal fade" id="receiptsHelp" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="receiptsHelpLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="receiptsHelpLabel">Receipts Help</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Purpose</h6>
                    <p>This screen manages inbound receipts and initial allocation into locations.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Index (List)</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Filter by warehouse, supplier, status, and received dates.</li>
                        <li>Use sorting and pagination to review large volumes.</li>
                        <li>Inactive receipts stay hidden unless explicitly included.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Create</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Create a receipt header with warehouse, receipt number, and supplier info.</li>
                        <li>Save to open the details screen for item allocation.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h6>Details & Items</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Add items by selecting product, lot, location, UoM, and quantity.</li>
                        <li>For lot-tracked SKUs, provide an existing lot or a new lot code.</li>
                        <li>For lot + expiry SKUs, expiration date is required when creating a new lot.</li>
                        <li>Locations must exist under the selected warehouse structure.</li>
                        <li>Click <strong>Complete Receipt</strong> to generate inventory balances.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h6>Common Issues</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li><strong>No locations:</strong> create sectors/sections/structures/locations first.</li>
                        <li><strong>Status locked:</strong> completed/canceled receipts cannot be edited.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-light border" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
